itle":"2026-07-XX","text":"<ul> <li>Docker\u8a2d\u5b9a\u8ffd\u52a0\u4e88\u5b9a</li> <li>\u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u69cb\u7bc9\u4e88\u5b9a</li> </ul>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/changelog/#_2","title":"\u4eca\u5f8c","text":"<p>\u69cb\u7bc9\u4f5c\u696d\u3092\u884c\u3063\u305f\u30bf\u30a4\u30df\u30f3\u30b0\u3067\u66f4\u65b0\u3059\u308b\u3002</p>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/commands/","title":"Linux\u30b3\u30de\u30f3\u30c9\u96c6","text":""},{"location":"07_maintenance/commands/#_1","title":"\u30b7\u30b9\u30c6\u30e0\u78ba\u8a8d","text":"<p>CPU\u78ba\u8a8d\uff1a</p> <pre><code>lscpu\n</code></pre> <p>\u30e1\u30e2\u30ea\u78ba\u8a8d\uff1a</p> <pre><code>free -h\n</code></pre> <p>\u30c7\u30a3\u30b9\u30af\u78ba\u8a8d\uff1a</p> <pre><code>df -h\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/commands/#_2","title":"\u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u7ba1\u7406","text":"<p>\u72b6\u614b\u78ba\u8a8d\uff1a</p> <pre><code>systemctl status \u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u540d\n</code></pre> <p>\u8d77\u52d5\uff1a</p> <pre><code>sudo systemctl start \u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u540d\n</code></pre> <p>\u505c\u6b62\uff1a</p> <pre><code>sudo systemctl stop \u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u540d\n</code></pre> <p>\u518d\u8d77\u52d5\uff1a</p> <pre><code>sudo systemctl restart \u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u540d\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/commands/#_3","title":"\u66f4\u65b0","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt update\n\nsudo apt upgrade\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/commands/#docker","title":"Docker","text":"<p>\u4e00\u89a7\uff1a</p> <pre><code>docker ps\n</code></pre> <p>\u30ed\u30b0\uff1a</p> <pre><code>docker logs \u30b3\u30f3\u30c6\u30ca\u540d\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"07_maintenance/todo/","title":"ToDo","text":""},{"location":"07_maintenance/todo/#_1","title":"\u672a\u5b9f\u65bd","text":""},{"location":"07_maintenance/todo/#_2","title":"\u7ba1\u7406\u74b0\u5883","text":"<ul> <li>[ ] Cockpit\u5c0e\u5165</li> <li>[ ] Portainer\u5c0e\u5165</li> <li>[ ] Homarr\u5c0e\u5165</li> </ul>"},{"loca